property_tycoon.model

Class PropertyLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • property_tycoon.model.PropertyLevel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<PropertyLevel>

    public final class PropertyLevel
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<PropertyLevel>
    This class represents a property level. Each property level belongs to a group and has a description. Property levels must be comparable to ensure integrity of game rules - namely that property levels of the same group can differ by no more than one at any time. For that reason, this class implements Comparable.
    Version:
    30/04/2018
    Author:
    meme-team
